WEBVTT

1
00:27:44.720 --> 00:27:46.240 
明白吗？
You understand?

2
00:27:47.240 --> 00:27:51.000 
你有男朋友吗？不，你没有男朋友
You got a boyfriend? No, you ain't got a boyfriend.

3
00:27:51.000 --> 00:27:53.800 
你可曾想过没有男朋友的原因？
You know why? Why don't you think you have a boyfriend?

4
00:27:53.800 --> 00:27:56.680 
因为你和街上的痞子鬼混
'Cause you're hangin' out with them coconuts on the corner.

5
00:27:56.680 --> 00:27:58.680 
和痞子鬼混没出息
You hang around coconuts, you get nowhere.

6
00:27:58.680 --> 00:28:00.280 
他们一无是处
They're lemons. Lemons.

7
00:28:00.320 --> 00:28:03.560 
与好人交往就会有好的朋友
You hang out with nice people, you get nice friends. You understand?

8
00:28:03.560 --> 00:28:06.080 
与聪明人交往就会有聪明的朋友
You hang out with smart people, you get smart friends.

9
00:28:06.080 --> 00:28:08.920 
与混混交往就会有混混朋友
　　　　　　　　　　　　  You hang out with yo-yo people, you get yo-yo friends.

10
00:28:08.920 --> 00:28:11.880 
这个道理很简单
You see, it's simple mathematics.

11
00:28:11.880 --> 00:28:13.680 
我希望你不会…我不会
　　　　　　　　　　  - I hope you ain't... - I won't.

12
00:28:13.680 --> 00:28:15.160 
我说的重点是？
What was I gonna say?

